				<td rowspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" style="text-align: justify;" width="100%" valign=top>
				<DIV>In the round room with the merchants, the regular vendor type NPCs are on the outside of the wall.&nbsp; The quest type NPCs (some of whom are also vendors, or at least Sateal is) are in the middle.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>So Tekrama for trader satchels is in the outside ring.&nbsp; Sateal for the Amulet quest is in the middle.&nbsp; Along with Caerlyna (to turn in bags) and others.&nbsp; The only quest related one not in the middle is the mage spell gnome (used to make Grandmaster Trophy no-rent bag into a permanent bag) who is in the tradeskill area for some reason.</DIV>
				
